title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file the second time.
EB: The out of sync message should not be displayed when overwriting the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file.
Expected result: The out of sync message should not be displayed.
